      "output": "=== TOP 15 LARGEST FILES IN DOWNLOADS ===\n2047.3 MB - Google AI Studio-20260623T104922Z-3-001.zip\n2012.5 MB - Google AI Studio-20260623T104922Z-3-003.zip\n1828.1 MB - Google AI Studio-20260623T104743Z-3-001.zip\n1753.1 MB - Google AI Studio-20260623T104922Z-3-005.zip\n1366.1 MB - iotbox-latest.zip\n943.5 MB - Non confermato 112308.crdownload\n611.6 MB - Non confermato 509695.crdownload\n420.3 MB - microsoft-edge.pdf\n402 MB - MiniMax Code Setup 3.0.35.exe\n400.5 MB - MiniMax Agent Setup 3.0.29.exe\n396 MB - mo-and-plam.zip\n366.8 MB - MiniMax Agent Setup 3.0.25.exe\n359.5 MB - AFJ weekly meeting - Jun 5 2026.mp4\n339.8 MB - Technical Bootcamp.zip\n198.7 MB - Non confermato 303746.crdownload\n",
