      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Now I have a clear picture. The Downloads folder alone has ~20.7 GB of files, many of which are duplicate/old installers and zip files. Let me also check for the MiniMax agent cache and Chrome cache more carefully.\n\nLet me compile a safe cleanup script that won't break anything.",
