    {
      "type": "answer",
      "text": "Here's the full picture:\n\n### Quick Cleanup Summary\n\n| What | Size | Safe to Delete? |\n|---|---|---|\n| 3 incomplete Chrome downloads (.crdownload) | **1.75 GB** | Yes -- junk |\n| 4 Google AI Studio duplicate zips | **7.64 GB** | Yes -- duplicates |\n| 3 MiniMax duplicate installers | **1.17 GB** | Yes -- keep newest only |\n| Chrome + Edge caches | **2.4 GB** | Yes -- regenerates |\n| Windows temp files | **0.47 GB** | Yes -- junk |\n| Crash dumps | **66 MB** | Yes -- old BSOD data |\n| MiniMax agent cache | **816 MB** | Yes -- regenerates |\n| **TOTAL** | **~14.3 GB** | |\n\n### Run these commands to clean up:",
