und($disk.FreeSpace/1GB,2)) GB free ($([math]::Round($disk.FreeSpace/$disk.Size*100,1))%)\\\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\\n\", \"description\": \"Clear remaining Chrome and Edge caches\"}",
