      "code": "{\"command\": \"# Unregister WSL Ubuntu to free 20.37 GB\\nWrite-Host \\\"Unregistering WSL Ubuntu...\\\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\\nwsl --unregister Ubuntu 2>&1\\nWrite-Host \\\"\\\"\\nWrite-Host \\\"Done!\\\" -ForegroundColor Green\\n\\n# Check new disk status\\n$disk = Get-WmiObject Win32_LogicalDisk -Filter \\\"DeviceID='C:'\\\"\\n$newFreeGB = [math]::Round($disk.FreeSpace / 1GB, 2)\\n$newPct = [math]::Round($disk.FreeSpace / $disk.Size * 100, 1)\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"\\\"\\nWrite-Host \\\"=============================================\\\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\\nWrite-Host \\\"  FINAL DISK STATUS\\\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\\nWrite-Host \\\"=============================================\\\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\\nWrite-Host \\\"  C: drive: $newFreeGB GB free ($newPct%)\\\" -ForegroundColor $(if ($newPct -ge 15) { \\\"Green\\\" } elseif ($newPct -ge 5) { \\\"Yellow\\\" } else { \\\"Red\\\" })\\nWrite-Host \\\"\\\"\\nWrite-Host \\\"  Before cleanup: 3.32 GB (0.7%)\\\" -ForegroundColor Red\\nWrite-Host \\\"  After cleanup:  $newFreeGB GB ($newPct%)\\\" -ForegroundColor $(if ($newPct -ge 15) { \\\"Green\\\" } elseif ($newPct -ge 5) { \\\"Yellow\\\" } else { \\\"Red\\\" })\\nWrite-Host \\\"  Space freed:    $([math]::Round($newFreeGB - 3.32, 2)) GB\\\" -ForegroundColor Green\\nWrite-Host \\\"=============================================\\\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\\n\", \"description\": \"Unregister WSL Ubuntu to free 20 GB\"}",
      "output": "Unregistering WSL Ubuntu...\nA\u0000n\u0000n\u0000u\u0000l\u0000l\u0000a\u0000m\u0000e\u0000n\u0000t\u0000o\u0000 \u0000r\u0000e\u0000g\u0000i\u0000s\u0000t\u0000r\u0000a\u0000z\u0000i\u0000o\u0000n\u0000e\u0000 \u0000i\u0000n\u0000 \u0000c\u0000o\u0000r\u0000s\u0000o\u0000.\u0000.\u0000.\u0000\r\u0000\r\u0000\n\u0000\nDone!\n\n=============================================\n  FINAL DISK STATUS\n=============================================\n  C: drive: 39.07 GB free (8.2%)\n\n  Before cleanup: 3.32 GB (0.7%)\n  After cleanup:  39.07 GB (8.2%)\n  Space freed:    35.75 GB\n=============================================\n",
