      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Excellent! We went from 3.32 GB (0.7%) to 39.07 GB (8.2%). That's a massive improvement - 35.75 GB freed! \n\n8.2% is much better than 0.7%, but ideally we want 15%+ for optimal BSOD prevention. However, this should be sufficient to stop the WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR crashes.\n\nLet me also clear the remaining caches (Chrome, HuggingFace, etc.) to get even more space.",
